{"tid":2338873,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"拿鐵鎚砸爛iPhone！具惠善看「螢幕整片碎裂」笑了","createTime":"2020-12-24T09:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T11:45:54.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"db929a816ffc2a7465a1f30551ff5ba02e061539","tid":2338873,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:27:34.000Z","msg":"南韓女星具惠善過去演出韓版《流星花園》「金絲草」走紅，她跟前夫安宰賢去年8月撕破臉，雙方上演分手擂台，直到今年才達成離婚協議。恢單後的具惠善持續她的創作，還開設經紀公司、辦畫展，不時會在社群網站分享生活，近日她參與綜藝錄製，竟拿鐵鎚砸爛手機，讓現場人全看傻眼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/24/2951732-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F24%2F2951732-PH.jpg&h=42f157f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼具惠善。（圖／翻攝自具惠善IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/24/2951754-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F24%2F2951754-PH.jpg&h=45793853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n具惠善近日參與了觀察型網路綜藝《Face ID》的錄製，向外界分享她的私下生活，20日節目公開預告片，只見具惠善穿著黑色羽絨外套出現在工作室，她突然拿起桌上的一把鐵鎚，接著蹲在地上掏出自己的iPhone手機，就在一旁工作人員滿臉困惑時，她終於開口：「就打一下。」具惠善把手機放地上，舉起鐵鎚往下砸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/24/2951724-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F24%2F2951724-PH.jpg&h=31e1d1dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼具惠善在節目中砸爛手機。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/24/2951725-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F24%2F2951725-PH.jpg&h=f06f0e1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n具惠善突然其來的舉動嚇壞讓工作人員全都驚呼，接著具惠善才解釋，她認為整理人際關係最好的方法，就是直接把手機摧毀，說完又拿著鐵鎚咚咚咚地敲了好幾下，直到螢幕完全碎裂，她爽朗一笑：「整個爛掉，就是我想要的樣子。」具惠善舉動引起網友討論，「這行為也太瘋了吧」、「說砸就砸，沒在客氣的」。<br />\n<br />\n也有粉絲出來緩頰，指出手機螢幕顯示了幾個字「破壞的美學」，認為具惠善身為藝術家，這應該是只是在展示一些行動藝術，到底真正前因後果為何，還是要看完整的節目才知道。"},{"pid":"93703293d9d76355fd86f5e8bf4a52f0c8b95ddd","tid":2338873,"uid":368454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:35:18.000Z","msg":"三小<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fccdce3f69de09ab3e468022036961acba61545","tid":2338873,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93703293d9d76355fd86f5e8bf4a52f0c8b95ddd","tid":2338873,"uid":368454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:35:18.000Z","msg":"三小<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:37:02.000Z","msg":"白卡婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d3c7590754a689088209f22abbbe4cb9b78290","tid":2338873,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:37:49.000Z","msg":"痴痴地..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f91f1dd3aed89b68b712391f4c66c7b91bf504a","tid":2338873,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:38:34.000Z","msg":"咁痴線個樣"},{"pid":"0e5e2fd634e170473c0daedd30c5348e237d14e8","tid":2338873,"uid":294121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:41:38.000Z","msg":"呢世人未屌過痴線婆算唔算失敗⋯"},{"pid":"efc3a70ba943248d3e9a75f08c36cbfc0d9763dc","tid":2338873,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1d3c7590754a689088209f22abbbe4cb9b78290","tid":2338873,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:37:49.000Z","msg":"痴痴地..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:42:25.000Z","msg":"入青山啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658e7b9b47c34f2cd65b430e3265d3c33ecd1ee6","tid":2338873,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e5e2fd634e170473c0daedd30c5348e237d14e8","tid":2338873,"uid":294121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:41:38.000Z","msg":"呢